information = An Ancient Vister Guardian is an Ancient colossal stone giant who guarded sacred mountain passes for millennia. Their immense strength and mastery over the earth make them a formidable foe. Legends say that The guardians were once a part of the mountain itself, brought to life by ancient magic to protect the land from invaders. Their deep connection with the earth grant them extraordinary abilities that allow them to manipulate the very ground they walk upon. 
notes = A Ancient Vister Guardian's unique abilities make them a powerful guardian of the mountains.

